source.name: Office of Adoption and Child Custody Advocacy  Performance Measures Fingerprints Clearance 2010
source.description: When an individual of family wish to adopt they must obtain fingerprint clearance.  This office is the pass through agency from the FBI, Illinois State Police, and the courts.
